{"post":{"id":"e9981eef-9819-4063-9573-d316e3cdae9b","title":"Gratuit ou Payant ?","excerpt":"Comprendre le modèle économique de Lalason Chez Lalason, plateforme pour les créateurs de contenu, nous croyons en la rémunération...","firstPublishedDate":"2024-12-16T10:15:12.680Z","lastPublishedDate":"2024-12-16T10:15:12.680Z","slug":"gratuit-ou-payant","featured":false,"pinned":false,"categoryIds":[],"memberId":"b3f3fbbd-9b4e-46c0-b0e4-7edc60705954","hashtags":[],"commentingEnabled":true,"minutesToRead":2,"tagIds":[],"relatedPostIds":[],"pricingPlanIds":[],"language":"fr","richContent":{"nodes":[{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"foo","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"1dlbm","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Comprendre le modèle économique de Lalason","decorations":[]}}],"headingData":{"level":2,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"g65ko48212","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"997tg","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Chez Lalason, plateforme pour les créateurs de contenu, nous croyons en la rémunération équitable des artistes, afin de les aider à mieux vivre de leur musique. Mais comment assurer la pérennité de notre modèle ? Nous vous expliquons ici les deux options qui s'offrent à vous pour profiter de notre bibliothèque musicale, selon que vous choisissiez de payer ou non.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"bq5uj","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"qwkv8355","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{}},{"type":"VIDEO","id":"qettf354","nodes":[],"videoData":{"video":{"src":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G_Ji3mi-kE0"},"duration":131.0},"thumbnail":{"src":{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/G_Ji3mi-kE0/maxresdefault.jpg"},"width":1280,"height":720},"title":"|Musique libre de droits| VDGL - Free"}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"6dlon356","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"84d6c","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"c5vcq","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"scp6d2075","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Option 1 : Utiliser Lalason gratuitement","decorations":[{"type":"FONT_SIZE","fontSizeData":{"unit":"PX","value":28}}]}}],"headingData":{"level":3,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"5utqd","nodes":[],"headingData":{"level":2,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"6a4lu","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Vous n'avez pas à dépenser un centime pour accéder à notre bibliothèque musicale ! C'est l'option \"gratuite\" qui s'appuie sur un principe simple : ","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"\"si un service est gratuit, c'est que vous êtes le produit.\"","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":" Concrètement, vous pouvez utiliser nos morceaux dans vos projets sans frais, mais avec une petite contrepartie :","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"sjkgj2754","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"9org32109","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Vous devrez ajouter la mention suivante dans la description de votre vidéo :","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"BLOCKQUOTE","id":"9k9ud2111","nodes":[{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"ntv7s2112","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Musique fournie par ","decorations":[{"type":"ITALIC","italicData":true}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"https://www.lalason.com","decorations":[{"type":"ITALIC","italicData":true},{"type":"LINK","linkData":{"link":{"url":"https://www.lalason.com","target":"BLANK"}}}]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}}],"blockquoteData":{"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"qobuq2115","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"xvbhw2787","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"En incluant cette phrase, vous nous aidez à faire connaître Lalason, et à soutenir les artistes qui contribuent à notre bibliothèque.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"ycmpy2818","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"5cqhg2117","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Mais ce n'est pas tout. Grâce à ","decorations":[]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Content ID","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":", le système de détection de YouTube, nous pouvons vérifier deux choses :","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"ORDERED_LIST","id":"1f62c2121","nodes":[{"type":"LIST_ITEM","id":"qj91m2122","nodes":[{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"g8chb2123","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Que la mention \"Musique fournie par Lalason\" est bien présente dans la description.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{}}]},{"type":"LIST_ITEM","id":"wgxdk2125","nodes":[{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"ljx822126","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Que vous avez utilisé un morceau provenant de notre plateforme.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"lrnlw2854","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{}}]}],"orderedListData":{"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"wxrno2128","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"En retour, nous récupérerons une partie de la monétisation de votre vidéo (généralement, c'est quelques centimes d'euros par vidéo). Ce modèle permet à Lalason de rémunérer les artistes tout en vous offrant un accès gratuit à une grande variété de musique.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"ecokd2130","nodes":[],"headingData":{"level":3,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"91dos","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"fnd5t","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Option 2 : Opter pour la version payante","decorations":[{"type":"FONT_SIZE","fontSizeData":{"unit":"PX","value":28}}]}}],"headingData":{"level":2,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"cd4sg5265","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"kd1ak5235","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"6np932157","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Si vous souhaitez utiliser nos morceaux sans avoir à ajouter la mention \"Musique fournie par Lalason\", ou si vous avez des projets à but commercial, l'option payante est faite pour vous.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"doafm5296","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"p8fgn2159","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"En choisissant cette option, vous bénéficiez de plusieurs avantages :","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"61bvs5327","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"BULLETED_LIST","id":"w8fez2161","nodes":[{"type":"LIST_ITEM","id":"1knyq2162","nodes":[{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"b8hdy2163","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"La possibilité de monétiser vos vidéos sans restrictions","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":".","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{}}]},{"type":"LIST_ITEM","id":"y5jct2166","nodes":[{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"2pxb52167","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Aucune mention obligatoire dans la description","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":".","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{}}]},{"type":"LIST_ITEM","id":"e85i72170","nodes":[{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"hlg7c2171","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Une licence d'utilisation pour tous vos projets commerciaux","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700}]}},{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":". Cela inclut les publicités TV, les génériques de films, les vidéos promotionnelles et tout autre projet monétisé. Pour ces types de projets, il est impératif de posséder une licence d'utilisation de nos morceaux.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{}}]}],"bulletedListData":{"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"izrzb5455","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"4awcd2174","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"En payant pour un abonnement, vous soutenez directement les artistes tout en bénéficiant d'une plus grande liberté d’utilisation pour vos projets.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"0dqx12176","nodes":[],"headingData":{"level":3,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"95v3a","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"HEADING","id":"1x08e2625","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Alors, quelle option choisir ?","decorations":[{"type":"FONT_SIZE","fontSizeData":{"unit":"PX","value":28}}]}}],"headingData":{"level":3,"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"6tw8g2658","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"riyz65516","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"ardtl2627","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Tout dépend de vos besoins ! Si vous êtes un créateur qui cherche à utiliser de la musique sans frais, l'option gratuite est une excellente solution. Vous faites ainsi la promotion de Lalason et contribuez à rémunérer les artistes. Si vous souhaitez un usage plus flexible et monétiser pleinement vos vidéos, l'option payante est la meilleure option.","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"ndtq22629","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Dans tous les cas, Lalason est là pour soutenir les créateurs, tout en assurant une rémunération juste pour les artistes. Découvrez notre bibliothèque musicale et choisissez l’option qui correspond le mieux à vos projets !","decorations":[]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"AUTO"}}}],"metadata":{"version":1,"createdTimestamp":"2024-03-27T13:00:21.536Z","updatedTimestamp":"2024-03-27T13:00:21.536Z","id":"b82e2b4e-88a0-40c7-b406-208e8d821480"},"documentStyle":{}},"preview":false,"contentId":"68235fdb9958032abf8ba3e5","mostRecentContributorId":"b3f3fbbd-9b4e-46c0-b0e4-7edc60705954","media":{"wixMedia":{"image":{"id":"b3f3fb_5f46858011eb49b1b270390ddfd184ef~mv2.jpg","url":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/b3f3fb_5f46858011eb49b1b270390ddfd184ef~mv2.jpg","height":1492,"width":2160,"filename":"ic_edited_edited.jpg"}},"displayed":true,"custom":true},"hasUnpublishedChanges":true,"translations":[],"customExcerpt":false,"internalCategoryIds":[],"internalRelatedPostIds":[]}}